import React from 'react'
import { Tool } from '../../container/Tool'
import { Picture } from '../../container/Picture'
import { Sidebar } from '../../container/Sidebar'
import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid'

export const Edit = () => {
    return (

        <Grid container >
            <Grid
                item
                xs={1}>
                <Sidebar />
            </Grid>
            <Grid
                item
                xs={2}>
                <Tool />
            </Grid>
            <Grid
                item>
                <Picture />
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    )
}
